g.text: source Programmable Logic Controller (PLC) suite that can create and run PLC
programs on custom hardware, such as a Raspberry Pi or an Arduino.
It consists of two main components, the Runtime and the Editor. The Editor was used to create our
main program using Ladder Logic programming, and the Runtime executes our program on the target
Runtime is installed and configured on both a Raspberry Pi 3B and an Arduino Mega 2560r3.
2560 is slaved to the Pi and only provides additional I/O for the system. All logic is run via the master
